column2: Nearly 5000 years after he was bestowed with the almighty powers of the Egyptian gods--and imprisoned just as quickly--Black Adam is freed from his earthly tomb and ready to unleash his unique form of justice on the modern world.
Dr. Rose must confront her troubling past after an accident in order to survive and escape her horrifying new reality.
